                                      "name": "execB",
                                      "fill": "#CCCCCC",
                                      "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                                      "width": "fill_container",
                                      "content": "A focused product for solo travelers offering verified local itineraries can capture underserved demand for authentic, non-touristy experiences. The strongest wedge is resident verification plus a solo-first UX that larger marketplaces do not prioritize.",
