                            {
                              "type": "frame",
                              "id": "rIu7l",
                              "name": "prdBodyD rendered markdown",
                              "width": "fill_container",
                              "layout": "vertical",
                              "gap": 22,
                              "children": [
                                {
                                  "type": "frame",
                                  "id": "AiFeE",
                                  "name": "Section I Introduction",
                                  "width": "fill_container",
                                  "layout": "vertical",
                                  "gap": 14,
                                  "children": [
                                    {
                                      "type": "text",
                                      "id": "vV7jl",
                                      "name": "h2 Introduction",
                                      "fill": "#0A0A0A",
                                      "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                                      "width": "fill_container",
                                      "content": "I. Introduction",
                                      "lineHeight": 1.05,
                                      "fontFamily": "Space Grotesk",
                                      "fontSize": 30,
                                      "fontWeight": "700"
                                    },
                                    {
                                      "type": "frame",
                                      "id": "6yKib",
                                      "name": "1.1 Background Information / Context",
                                      "width": "fill_container",
                                      "layout": "vertical",
                                      "gap": 10,
                                      "children": [
                                        {
                                          "type": "text",
                                          "id": "Eoqol",
                                          "name": "h3 Background",
                                          "fill": "#0A0A0A",
                                          "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                                          "width": "fill_container",
                                          "content": "1.1 Background Information / Context",
                                          "lineHeight": 1.2,
                                          "fontFamily": "Space Grotesk",
                                          "fontSize": 20,
                                          "fontWeight": "600"
                                        },
                                        {
                                          "type": "text",
                                          "id": "lPCky",
                                          "name": "paragraph",
                                          "fill": "#444444",
                                          "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                                          "width": "fill_container",
                                          "content": "The travel industry has experienced significant shifts toward authentic, experiential travel, with 76% of millennials preferring to spend money on experiences rather than material goods. However, the current digital travel ecosystem remains dominated by platforms that prioritize mainstream tourist attractions and commercially bookable experiences. This has created a substantial market gap for travelers seeking genuine local immersion.",
                                          "lineHeight": 1.6,
                                          "fontFamily": "Inter",
                                          "fontSize": 13,
                                          "fontWeight": "normal"
                                        },
                                        {
                                          "type": "text",
                                          "id": "ivkU4",
                                          "name": "paragraph",
                                          "fill": "#444444",
                                          "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                                          "width": "fill_container",
                                          "content": "The rise of solo travel, accounting for 25% of all trips globally, combined with increased comfort with mobile-first platforms, creates room for a differentiated approach. Current market leaders like Wanderlog, Viator, and GetYourGuide excel at logistics and popular attractions but fail to surface the hyperlocal, non-commercialized experiences that define authentic cultural immersion.",
                                          "lineHeight": 1.6,
                                          "fontFamily": "Inter",
                                          "fontSize": 13,
                                          "fontWeight": "normal"
                                        },
                                        {
                                          "type": "text",
                                          "id": "sx6rY",
                                          "name": "paragraph",
                                          "fill": "#444444",
                                          "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                                          "width": "fill_container",
                                          "content": "LocalLens positions itself at the intersection of community-driven content curation and personalized travel planning, leveraging the creator economy and local expertise to solve a persistent pain point in independent travel.",
                                          "lineHeight": 1.6,
                                          "fontFamily": "Inter",
                                          "fontSize": 13,
                                          "fontWeight": "normal"
                                        }
                                      ]
                                    },
                                    {
                                      "type": "frame",
                                      "id": "EXzuO",
                                      "name": "1.2 Problem Definition / User Needs",
                                      "width": "fill_container",
                                      "layout": "vertical",
                                      "gap": 10,
                                      "children": [
                                        {
                                          "type": "text",
                                          "id": "5jOOh",
                                          "name": "h3 Problem Definition",
                                          "fill": "#0A0A0A",
                                          "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                                          "width": "fill_container",
                                          "content": "1.2 Problem Definition / User Needs",
                                          "lineHeight": 1.2,
                                          "fontFamily": "Space Grotesk",
                                          "fontSize": 20,
                                          "fontWeight": "600"
                                        },
                                        {
                                          "type": "text",
                                          "id": "6DInJ",
                                          "name": "strong Primary Problems",
                                          "fill": "#0A0A0A",
                                          "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                                          "width": "fill_container",
                                          "content": "Primary Problems Identified",
                                          "lineHeight": 1.4,
                                          "fontFamily": "Inter",
                                          "fontSize": 13,
                                          "fontWeight": "700"
                                        },
                                        {
                                          "type": "frame",
                                          "id": "bC0nr",
                                          "name": "Primary problems list",
                                          "width": "fill_container",
                                          "layout": "vertical",
                                          "gap": 6,
                                          "children": [
                                            {
                                              "type": "text",
                                              "id": "6WYxG",
                                              "name": "bullet",
                                              "fill": "#444444",
                                              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                                              "width": "fill_container",
                                              "content": "• Solo travelers still end up at overcrowded tourist attractions despite seeking authentic experiences.",
                                              "lineHeight": 1.45,
                                              "fontFamily": "Inter",
                                              "fontSize": 13,
                                              "fontWeight": "normal"
                                            },
                                            {
                                              "type": "text",
                                              "id": "xaw1D",
                                              "name": "bullet",
                                              "fill": "#444444",
                                              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                                              "width": "fill_container",
                                              "content": "• Existing platforms are biased toward mainstream, bookable activities.",
                                              "lineHeight": 1.45,
                                              "fontFamily": "Inter",
                                              "fontSize": 13,
                                              "fontWeight": "normal"
                                            },
                                            {
                                              "type": "text",
                                              "id": "QRkEb",
                                              "name": "bullet",
                                              "fill": "#444444",
                                              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                                              "width": "fill_container",
                                              "content": "• Verified locals-only trust signals are weak or missing.",
                                              "lineHeight": 1.45,
                                              "fontFamily": "Inter",
                                              "fontSize": 13,
                                              "fontWeight": "normal"
                                            },
                                            {
                                              "type": "text",
                                              "id": "7zrQe",
                                              "name": "bullet",
                                              "fill": "#444444",
                                              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                                              "width": "fill_container",
                                              "content": "• Micro, non-bookable experiences like neighborhood bars, street markets, and community events are underrepresented.",
                                              "lineHeight": 1.45,
                                              "fontFamily": "Inter",
                                              "fontSize": 13,
                                              "fontWeight": "normal"
                                            },
                                            {
                                              "type": "text",
                                              "id": "dNaFf",
                                              "name": "bullet",
                                              "fill": "#444444",
                                              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                                              "width": "fill_container",
                                              "content": "• Neighborhood-first discovery, hyperlocal granularity, and contextual guidance are all weak.",
                                              "lineHeight": 1.45,
                                              "fontFamily": "Inter",
                                              "fontSize": 13,
                                              "fontWeight": "normal"
                                            }
                                          ]
                                        },
                                        {
                                          "type": "text",
                                          "id": "20qBQ",
                                          "name": "strong Unmet User Needs",
                                          "fill": "#0A0A0A",
                                          "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                                          "width": "fill_container",
                                          "content": "Unmet User Needs",
                                          "lineHeight": 1.4,
                                          "fontFamily": "Inter",
                                          "fontSize": 13,
                                          "fontWeight": "700"
                                        },
                                        {
                                          "type": "frame",
                                          "id": "fbNIc",
                                          "name": "Unmet user needs list",
                                          "width": "fill_container",
                                          "layout": "vertical",
                                          "gap": 6,
                                          "children": [
                                            {
                                              "type": "text",
                                              "id": "EfCXT",
                                              "name": "bullet",
                                              "fill": "#444444",
                                              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                                              "width": "fill_container",
                                              "content": "• Access to vetted local knowledge beyond guidebooks",
                                              "lineHeight": 1.45,
                                              "fontFamily": "Inter",
                                              "fontSize": 13,
                                              "fontWeight": "normal"
                                            },
                                            {
                                              "type": "text",
                                              "id": "AOtYj",
                                              "name": "bullet",
                                              "fill": "#444444",
                                              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                                              "width": "fill_container",
                                              "content": "• Curated itineraries featuring experiences locals actually enjoy",
                                              "lineHeight": 1.45,
                                              "fontFamily": "Inter",
                                              "fontSize": 13,
                                              "fontWeight": "normal"
                                            },
                                            {
                                              "type": "text",
                                              "id": "CBysW",
                                              "name": "bullet",
                                              "fill": "#444444",
                                              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                                              "width": "fill_container",
                                              "content": "• Neighborhood-level discovery with walking and transit optimized routes",
                                              "lineHeight": 1.45,
                                              "fontFamily": "Inter",
                                              "fontSize": 13,
                                              "fontWeight": "normal"
                                            },
                                            {
                                              "type": "text",
                                              "id": "QuVJT",
                                              "name": "bullet",
                                              "fill": "#444444",
                                              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                                              "width": "fill_container",
                                              "content": "• Cultural context, etiquette guidance, and seasonal recommendations",
                                              "lineHeight": 1.45,
                                              "fontFamily": "Inter",
                                              "fontSize": 13,
                                              "fontWeight": "normal"
                                            }
                                          ]
                                        },
                                        {
                                          "type": "text",
                                          "id": "S1Jir",
                                          "name": "strong Representative Personas",
                                          "fill": "#0A0A0A",
                                          "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                                          "width": "fill_container",
                                          "content": "Representative Personas",
                                          "lineHeight": 1.4,
                                          "fontFamily": "Inter",
                                          "fontSize": 13,
                                          "fontWeight": "700"
                                        },
                                        {
                                          "type": "text",
                                          "id": "RyMtc",
                                          "name": "paragraph",
                                          "fill": "#444444",
                                          "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                                          "width": "fill_container",
                                          "content": "The document covers solo travelers seeking authentic trips, efficient weekend explorers who want insider guidance, and budget-conscious sabbatical travelers who need confidence, meaning, and affordability.",
                                          "lineHeight": 1.6,
                                          "fontFamily": "Inter",
                                          "fontSize": 13,
                                          "fontWeight": "normal"
                                        }
                                      ]
                                    }
                                  ]
                                },
                                {
                                  "type": "frame",
                                  "id": "t2Hiv",
                                  "name": "Section IV Features and Functionality",
                                  "width": "fill_container",
                                  "layout": "vertical",
                                  "gap": 14,
                                  "children": [
                                    {
                                      "type": "text",
                                      "id": "h4QAj",
                                      "name": "h2 Features",
                                      "fill": "#0A0A0A",
                                      "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                                      "width": "fill_container",
                                      "content": "IV. Features and Functionality",
                                      "lineHeight": 1.05,
                                      "fontFamily": "Space Grotesk",
                                      "fontSize": 30,
                                      "fontWeight": "700"
                                    },
                                    {
                                      "type": "frame",
                                      "id": "joiNH",
                                      "name": "4.1 Requirements",
                                      "width": "fill_container",
                                      "layout": "vertical",
                                      "gap": 10,
                                      "children": [
                                        {
                                          "type": "text",
                                          "id": "2N5z7",
                                          "name": "h3 Requirements",
                                          "fill": "#0A0A0A",
                                          "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                                          "width": "fill_container",
                                          "content": "4.1 Requirements",
                                          "lineHeight": 1.2,
                                          "fontFamily": "Space Grotesk",
                                          "fontSize": 20,
                                          "fontWeight": "600"
                                        },
                                        {
                                          "type": "text",
                                          "id": "gDdxC",
                                          "name": "strong Functional Requirements",
                                          "fill": "#0A0A0A",
                                          "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                                          "width": "fill_container",
                                          "content": "Functional Requirements",
                                          "lineHeight": 1.4,
                                          "fontFamily": "Inter",
                                          "fontSize": 13,
                                          "fontWeight": "700"
                                        },
                                        {
                                          "type": "text",
                                          "id": "LcfeG",
                                          "name": "paragraph",
                                          "fill": "#444444",
                                          "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                                          "width": "fill_container",
                                          "content": "User registration and profile management, local curator onboarding and verification, custom itinerary generation, community recommendation submission and curation, one-time itinerary payments, ratings and reviews, messaging, offline map support, notifications, and admin moderation.",
                                          "lineHeight": 1.6,
                                          "fontFamily": "Inter",
                                          "fontSize": 13,
                                          "fontWeight": "normal"
                                        },
                                        {
                                          "type": "text",
                                          "id": "enhY9",
                                          "name": "strong Non-Functional Requirements",
                                          "fill": "#0A0A0A",
                                          "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                                          "width": "fill_container",
                                          "content": "Non-Functional Requirements",
                                          "lineHeight": 1.4,
                                          "fontFamily": "Inter",
                                          "fontSize": 13,
                                          "fontWeight": "700"
                                        },
                                        {
                                          "type": "text",
                                          "id": "skQXe",
                                          "name": "paragraph",
                                          "fill": "#444444",
                                          "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                                          "width": "fill_container",
                                          "content": "Page loads under 2 seconds, 99.9% uptime, secure payment handling, scalability to 10,000 concurrent users, mobile optimization, and WCAG 2.1 AA accessibility.",
                                          "lineHeight": 1.6,
                                          "fontFamily": "Inter",
                                          "fontSize": 13,
                                          "fontWeight": "normal"
                                        },
                                        {
                                          "type": "text",
                                          "id": "L7zvb",
                                          "name": "strong Integration Requirements",
                                          "fill": "#0A0A0A",
                                          "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                                          "width": "fill_container",
                                          "content": "Integration Requirements",
                                          "lineHeight": 1.4,
                                          "fontFamily": "Inter",
                                          "fontSize": 13,
                                          "fontWeight": "700"
                                        },
                                        {
                                          "type": "text",
                                          "id": "mKOEk",
                                          "name": "paragraph",
                                          "fill": "#444444",
                                          "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                                          "width": "fill_container",
                                          "content": "Google Maps, Stripe, SendGrid, analytics tooling, and content management for curator-generated content.",
                                          "lineHeight": 1.6,
                                          "fontFamily": "Inter",
                                          "fontSize": 13,
                                          "fontWeight": "normal"
                                        }
                                      ]
                                    },
                                    {
                                      "type": "frame",
                                      "id": "3Lkjz",
                                      "name": "4.2 User Stories / Use Cases",
                                      "width": "fill_container",
                                      "layout": "vertical",
                                      "gap": 10,
                                      "children": [
                                        {
                                          "type": "text",
                                          "id": "5Aisq",
                                          "name": "h3 User Stories",
                                          "fill": "#0A0A0A",
                                          "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                                          "width": "fill_container",
                                          "content": "4.2 User Stories / Use Cases",
                                          "lineHeight": 1.2,
                                          "fontFamily": "Space Grotesk",
                                          "fontSize": 20,
                                          "fontWeight": "600"
                                        },
                                        {
                                          "type": "frame",
                                          "id": "7BIoS",
                                          "name": "numbered user stories",
                                          "width": "fill_container",
                                          "layout": "vertical",
                                          "gap": 6,
                                          "children": [
                                            {
                                              "type": "text",
                                              "id": "hEeOq",
                                              "name": "numbered item",
                                              "fill": "#444444",
                                              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                                              "width": "fill_container",
                                              "content": "1. Buy a custom itinerary and experience a city like a resident, not a tourist.",
                                              "lineHeight": 1.45,
                                              "fontFamily": "Inter",
                                              "fontSize": 13,
                                              "fontWeight": "normal"
                                            },
                                            {
                                              "type": "text",
